snippet.title: Parachute(Atari 2600)Full Unedited Playthrough(Every Difficulty Skill)
snippet.description:
Managed this in around half an hour of playing it. Even though it will cycle through the difficulty on its own like the Smurf one, that game doesn't have a specific meter telling me at all times what difficulty level I started off with. It has to be manually adjusted, and since this is an unedited playthrough I showed all of that completely, and made sure that I showed I was resetting the game each time to change the difficulty. In my head I could hear the comments, and I wasn't quite comfortable with the idea of the meter staying the way it was either, so there you go.
